main event: A woman in Mequon, Wisconsin reported seeing an oval-shaped object with lights hovering over her residence on May 9, 1965 around 8:30 PM.
interesting points: The object hovered for 3-4 minutes before rapidly moving off to the west in a straight line.
The object made a humming noise.
The witness, Mrs. Russell, reported the sighting to the Air Force.
The Air Force could not identify the object as any conventional aircraft or known natural phenomena.
The witness was familiar with scientific lasers and did not believe the object was related to that technology.
